        </mxCell>
        
        <mxCell id="summary-text" value="1. Client Request → Entry Point (index.ts) → Express App Setup&#xa;2. Middleware Chain → Timestamp → Locale → Logging → Query Validation → Introspection Control&#xa;3. Request Routing → GraphQL (Apollo Server) | REST (Express Routes)&#xa;4. GraphQL Directives → Authentication → Authorization → Rate Limiting → Permission Checks&#xa;5. Module Layer → Resolvers (User, Config, Role, Event, Notification, UI-Label) → Services&#xa;6. Shared Libraries → Auth Utils, Error Handler, Email/SMS Services, AWS, Firebase, Elasticsearch, Queue System&#xa;7. Data Layer → Sequelize ORM → Database Models → PostgreSQL Database&#xa;8. Caching &amp; Background → Redis (Sessions, Rate Limits, Queue Storage) → Background Job Processing&#xa;9. External Integrations → AWS S3/CloudFront, Twilio/MSG91, Sendbay, Firebase, Pusher, Elasticsearch, Sentry" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
